{"tid":2252044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(有大陸市場唔怕) 吉野家屢成攻擊對象 母企內地分店多近10倍","createTime":"2020-10-21T08:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T10:33:22.000Z","uid":522,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9d2e32b8b41e67c54a0e138b657c0a549e7b0fdb","tid":2252044,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2475000/2478883/20191021_clp_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2475000%2F2478883%2F20191021_clp_1024.jpg&h=7376f70a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>合興內地店舖多近9倍 經營具挑戰</strong><br />\n事實上，洪明基家族旗下洪氏集團在中港都與日本吉野家合作經營，在香港經營60家吉野家分店，另外透過合興 （00047） 在華北等地特許經營。內地和香港吉野家分開經營，上市公司和香港吉野家沒從屬關係。<br />\n<br />\n據合興最新中期報告，集團在內地一共有576家分店，當中369家屬吉野家品牌，較去年同期增加12家分店。<br />\n<br />\n換言之，吉野家在本港總共有60家分店，同一集團在內地分店數目香港近10倍。<br />\n<br />\n雖然內地分店數目遠多於香港，惟公司在內地經營也遇到挑戰，合興上半財年純利為5,680.9萬元，按年跌7.7%，以收入計，吉野家銷售錄得收入8.6億元，佔集團整體超過8成。以公司576家分店計算，每間店鋪半年盈利能力僅9.86萬元，可見經營挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n內地每間店半年賺10萬 近4個月股價跌逾3成<br />\n<br />\n合興近月股價急轉弱，最新價較年內高位大幅回落3分之1。公司今日跌逾6%，報0.108港元，至下午3時成交金額僅2,160港元，成交數量為20,000股。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PW50vmx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPW50vmx.png&h=f6ff5573&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7af5c1fe4b357b175fbc1b82f5f3a5186c769f9b","tid":2252044,"uid":55519,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:16:41.000Z","msg":"建議執左香港分店 發展大灣區 共享祖國榮耀"},{"pid":"52ad5c0a64dd5d07bc48ec7403884389554f8f38","tid":2252044,"uid":247471,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:18:21.000Z","msg":"好呀，靠強國睇下最後邊個死"},{"pid":"184319ae88a653aaa51c095b59dfb26890863f0e","tid":2252044,"uid":522,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rOAPoHR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrOAPoHR.png&h=3802a352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有3億燒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205fe8825346148cbdefb3cf249eb4d2d197eafa","tid":2252044,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"成年冇食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇住執咗幾間人都開心咗"},{"pid":"d1c1f7886ee2fa6ba936d13eaef0d119fe1e6970","tid":2252044,"uid":185656,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:23:18.000Z","msg":"精日分子唔食真功夫?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9259113a07bfc690dda03fee449532b36c4ca3f3","tid":2252044,"uid":62749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"惟公司在內地經營也遇到挑戰，<br />\n<br />\n合興上半財年純利為5,680.9萬元，按年跌7.7%，<br />\n<br />\n以收入計，吉野家銷售錄得收入8.6億元，佔集團整體超過8成。<br />\n<br />\n以公司576家分店計算，每間店鋪半年盈利能力僅9.86萬元，<br />\n<br />\n可見經營挑戰。"},{"pid":"4520e494d30e68ec00a35f655ae4b705eca0e1a4","tid":2252044,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"中国人有吉野家食唔洗食草啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ee3772f81b9bb97b4f7c6e1f665660525fa47d","tid":2252044,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9259113a07bfc690dda03fee449532b36c4ca3f3","tid":2252044,"uid":62749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"惟公司在內地經營也遇到挑戰，<br />\n<br />\n合興上半財年純利為5,680.9萬元，按年跌7.7%，<br />\n<br />\n以收入計，吉野家銷售錄得收入8.6億元，佔集團整體超過8成。<br />\n<br />\n以公司576家分店計算，每間店鋪半年盈利能力僅9.86萬元，<br />\n<br />\n可見經營挑戰。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"上年新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今年大蝕"},{"pid":"6cad8a3d2c881582622b901c29a809c3fd7293d8","tid":2252044,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyT